18.18: ninb Bua heug huvb tiaj uaq zang maaib kruj huvb ting Eei tomb Jyen, hin-Ki-yaa, Eei txn, e-li-yaa-Kim, Zauj sepq-naa srub piuq Zauj aa-saapg Eei txn, fiaq srub taan Eei Jyen uaq taub yo-aa, Zwrtq mivb pwavb ninb Bua.
18.8: ninb Bx'q hivb fi-li-saa-tia myenb, zuvq Bx'q Tauj kaa-saa Zauj Wiv Rwrnj Eei txvj, yem maaib laaub Eei txvj Tauj maaib zivb laatg weib wrnq Eei txvj.
18.33: maaib haiq nxm kua'q Eei haiq taub zyenb Fruj Jiaj kanb Eei kua'q pyauj Dutq atg-si-lia huvb Eei puab Diaq?
18.3: ziuj zyruq mavg, he-se-Ki-yaa zruj tu'q hxpg Navq ninb Eei ovb Taaij, Daa-witq, zruj Eei Euvb Euvg.
18.32: zuaq yia txb meib Bua mivb Tauj nxm teib puv Navq meib Bua kanb Eei teib puv nx. se maaib laavb zi'g, maaib syavb a'vung tiuq Eei teib puv, maaib Fuaq, maaib a'vung Wivj Eei teib puv, maaib ka'lanq Dyavj Zauj mweib txvb Eei teib puv, weig pun meib Bua maaib mcvg zyavb, maiq zeid zu'g taig.’ “he-se-Ki-yaa kxvq, ‘zyruq zuvq xij Fruj yia Bua,’ uaq teij waag meib Bua maiq tuvq mwavj weig zu'g ninb Kuvj Duaq meib Bua Navq.
18.21: mavg maa'b! meib Kauj i-yipq se Navq Kauj lua'g ti'g kwcvb Baaij zruj pyaab Byaag yavb Jauq nx, haib pa'q zu'g puad mun. i-yipq Eei faa-lo huvb yaag Navq naaiq nx zruj pun yetg zuvq pavg ninb Eei myenb.
18.35: sij kxvq naaiq teij kua'q Eei yetg zuvq zyenb maiq maaib haiq taub Fruj tu'q ninb Eei kua'q pyauj Dutq yia Eei puab Diaq, uaq Euvg zyruq fuvg haib Fruj ye-lu-saa-lem Zwrtq yia Eei puab Diaq?”
18.14: yu-Daa Eei huvb, he-se-Ki-yaa, zyrug Paaiq myenb mivb laa-Kitq Tauj atg-si-lia Eei huvb uaq. ninb kxvq, “yia zruj txvg mig a'q. Toq meib Twij Gxi maiq tuvq Bx'q yia. meib xij yia pwib Bu'ziaj yia zyrug pun a'q.” atg-si-lia Eei huvb zyrug heug yu-Daa Eei huvb, he-se-Ki-yaa, Zwrtq Ju'q Zin yetg pc'q Juaq zyepg Jxib Eaanb Zauj lua'g pc'q zyepg Juaq Jxib Jyem.
18.23: “+‘ib zang meib Zauj yia Eei zyruq, atg-si-lia Eei huvb, Druq kaaj. sij kxvq meib lxd tu'q myenb kauj keb nx, yia pun i Zin taub maad meib.
18.6: ninb Kauj wrnq zyruq, zanb zang kan lovj ninb, maiq kwavg. he-se-Ki-yaa ei Jyenq zyruq Jiu pun mo-se Eei leib latg.
18.34: haa-matq Zauj aan-patg muvq Eei zyenb yem haaij? sej-faan-waa-im, he-naa Zauj ipg-waa muvq Eei zyenb yem haaij? ninb Bua Fruj saa-maa-lia leib Dutq yia Eei puab Diaq fai?
18.2: faauj weig zruj huvb uaq zang, ninb tu'q Eig zyepg Mmd Havj. ninb yem ye-lu-saa-lem kunq Eig zyepg Juaq Havj. ninb Eei maa se sej-Kaa-li-yaa Eei sia'q, Buaj heug aa-Bi-yaa.
18.36: mq paag pc'g fivj sekq Ria'g Eei, maiq tau yetg Jruj, weig zu'g huvb tiaj hatg ninb Bua, “maiq tuvq tau ninb.”
18.20: meib Namq taaib Kuvj lovg pc'g waag Navq haib maaib za'eij, maaib Qa'q Bx'q Jaaj fai? meib Kauj haiq taub Zivj taaib vcvg yia?
18.24: sij kxvq meib Kauj i-yipq Eei Bx'q Jaaj maab Zia Zauj keb maad pcv, meib fuvg haib Bx'q tu'q hivb yia Eei zyruq Eei yetg taub kaub faij Jiaj Eei pcvb pyeiq?
18.28: uaq taub tomb pcvb pyeiq zyrug sruq Jiad taaib lovg yu-Daa myenb Eei waag heug Jyenq kxvq, “xij zu'g mwavj tomb ziub huvb, se atg-si-lia Eei huvb, Eei waag maa'b!
18.7: zyruq Zauj ninb yem. ninb haiq zang Zwrtq mivb zruj haiq Euvg, ninb zruj tu'q Zwrtq Eei. ninb vcvg Jyenq maiq fub suj atg-si-lia Eei huvb.
18.29: huvb tiaj Navq naaiq nx kxvq, ‘maiq tuvq mwavj he-se-Ki-yaa Duaq meib Bua. ninb maiq haib Fruj meib Bua leib Dutq yia Eei puab Diaq.
18.19: maaib taub uaq teij tomb pcvb pyeiq kxvq Buaj ninb Bua, “xij zu'g Buaj he-se-Ki-yaa, “+‘tomb ziub huvb, atg-si-lia Eei huvb, Navq naaiq nx kxvq, “meib Kauj haiq Euvg?
18.17: atg-si-lia Eei huvb Paaiq pua taub ninb Eei Lo Jiaj Eei pcvb pyeiq Zauj Jyenq pcvb kwanb Zamq Eei yem laa-Kitq mivb Tauj ye-lu-saa-lem, he-se-Ki-yaa huvb uaq. mivb Tauj ye-lu-saa-lem, ninb Bua tivb Jyenq yem uaq Jiaj puv Eei uamb tomb Eei zwrnj, Eomg Dia Eei Zyavq uaq tiub Jauq.
18.31: “maiq tuvq mwavj he-se-Ki-yaa Eei waag. atg-si-lia Eei huvb kxvq, ‘Zwrtq taaib lxd yia maa'b! Zauj yia kxvq hxpg. kx'g myenb zyrug tu'q Eang kx'g myenb Eei a'vung Mei Eei pyruq. kx'g myenb tu'q Eang kx'g myenb Eei vovb Exj Dyavj Eei pyruq yaag hopq kanb Eei syru uamb Kwrtq Eei uam.
18.30: maiq tuvq mwavj he-se-Ki-yaa Duaq meib Bua Kauj zyruq. ninb xij kxvq, “zyruq Dovg haaij zuvq xij Fruj yia Bua. ninb maiq zx'q naaiq nxm zivb Jiu pun yem atg-si-lia huvb Eei puab Diaq.”+’
18.27: mq paag uaq taub pcvb pyeiq kxvq, “yia Eei zyruq Paaiq yia taaib Kuvj xij yia Zauj meib Eei zyruq Zauj meib Bua kanb kxvq fai? se lyemb zweid Jyenq zivb laatg uaq teij xij zu'g Zauj meib Bua Eang ninb Bua kanb Eei Gaiq, hopq ninb Bua kanb Eei yiad maiq zeid?”
18.11: atg-si-lia Eei huvb kwaatq i-saa-laa-en myenb mivb atg-si-lia kua'q, pun ninb Bua yem haa-laa-aa Zauj ko-saan teig Eei haa-Bo Daaib Len Zauj mi-Dia myenb Eei muvq.
18.5: he-se-Ki-yaa Kauj zyruq, i-saa-laa-en myenb Eei Tinb huvb. Navq naaig, yem yu-Daa Eei yetg zuvq huvb, maiq kunq zinb Daavg Eei Zauj Ga'haaq Eei, maiq maaib haiq taub Navq ninb.
18.9: he-se-Ki-yaa zruj huvb ta'feij Havj uaq Havj, se e-laa Eei txn, ho-se-yaa, zruj i-saa-laa-en Eei huvb ta'Zyetq Havj uaq Havj, atg-si-lia Eei huvb, scn-maa-ne-sej, Zwrtq mivb weib Jyenq xij Bx'q saa-maa-lia zivb.
18.16: uaq zang yu-Daa Eei huvb, he-se-Ki-yaa, mc'q Revg tovb ninb pwav Jyenq zavg zyruq Eei pyauq Eei kcvb Zauj kcvb zrug Eei Jyem, fuvj pun atg-si-lia Eei huvb.
18.37: kruj huvb ting uaq taub Jyen, hin-Ki-yaa Eei txn, e-li-yaa-Kim, Zauj sepq-naa srub piuq Zauj aa-saapg Eei txn, fiaq srub taan Eei Jyen uaq taub yo-aa, zyrug petq kanb Eei lwib hruj cvj mivb Tauj he-se-Ki-yaa uaq, yaag txb uaq taub tomb pcvb pyeiq Eei waag mivb kxvq Buaj ninb.
18.4: ninb Zc'q Zwrtq yem Lav zavg zyenb Eei txvj, Bx'q huq zavg zyenb Eei la'pyeib tovg yaag kxij aa-se-laa zyenb Eeid Eei Dyavb favj. ninb Bx'q huq mo-se zruj taaib Eei tovb si'q naav, weig zu'g Tauj uaq teij Nxib Eia'g i-saa-laa-en myenb Zxg puaq huv pun uaq tiub naav. uaq tiub naav, myenb heug ne-hutg-Taan.
18.10: Jiaj liud pua Havj uaq Havj, atg-si-lia myenb Zaavq tu'q uaq nxm zivb mig a'q. saa-maa-lia zu'g Zaavq uaq zang, he-se-Ki-yaa zruj ye-lu-saa-lem Eei huvb ta'lua'g Havj, ho-se-yaa zruj i-saa-laa-en Eei huvb ta'Juaq Havj.
18.22: sij kxvq meib Buaj yia, ‘yia Bua Kauj zyruq, yia Bua Eei Tinb huvb,’ he-se-Ki-yaa Zc'q kwavg uaq teij yem Lav zavg zyenb Eei txvj Zauj ziab txvb se naaiq taub Tinb huvb Eei maiq zeid? he-se-Ki-yaa Zxg kxvq Buaj yu-Daa Zauj ye-lu-saa-lem Eei myenb, ‘meib Bua xij zu'g yem ye-lu-saa-lem naaiq nxm ziab txvb ziag.’+”
18.12: naaiq teij sig Zwrtq taaib weig zu'g ninb Bua maiq mwavj zyruq, ninb Bua Eei Tinb huvb, Eei waag. ninb Bua vcvg Jyenq ninb Bua Zauj ninb lcvd Jiaj Eei vcvg waag, tovb zyruq Eei pru, mo-se, hatg Eei waag. ninb Bua maiq mwavj yaag maiq ei Jyenq zruj.
18.15: he-se-Ki-yaa zyrug zx'q yem zavg zyruq Eei pyauq Zauj huvb ting syru Jaaij Eei ka'naaiq Eei txvj Eei yetg zuvq Eaanb fuvj pun ninb.
18.13: he-se-Ki-yaa zruj huvb zyepg feij Havj uaq Havj, atg-si-lia Eei huvb, sen-naa-Ke-lipq, taaib Bx'q yu-Daa maaib zivb laatg wrnq Eei yetg zuvq zivb yaag Zaavq tu'q mig a'q.
18.1: e-laa Eei txn, ho-se-yaa, zruj i-saa-laa-en Eei huvb ta'faam Havj uaq Havj, aa-hatg Eei txn, he-se-Ki-yaa, faauj weig zruj yu-Daa Eei huvb.
18.26: hin-Ki-yaa Eei txn, e-li-yaa-Kim, Zauj sepq-naa Zauj yo-aa kxvq Buaj uaq taub tomb pcvb pyeiq, “Toq lovg aa-lam waag Zauj yia Bua, meib Eei pru, kxvq waag weig zu'g yia Bua pia'g Hruq Eei. maiq tuvq lovg yu-Daa myenb Eei waag pun yem zivb laatg kub vwaaig Eei pc'g fivj haib mwavj haid.”
18.25: maiq taan Bua'g naaiq. yia taaib Bx'q paaig naaiq nxm teib puv se maiq maaib zyruq Zauj yia taaib fai? zyruq kanb kxvq Buaj yia Zwrtq mivb myetg naaiq nxm teib puv maa'b!’+”

8.18: ninb ei Jyenq i-saa-laa-en Eei huvb Eei za'eij, se Navq aa-hapg uaq pyauq myenb, weig zu'g ninb lovg aa-hapg Eei sia'q zruj auq. ziuj zyruq mavg ninb zruj waaig sig.
8.8: huvb tiaj zyrug Buaj haa-saa-en. “txb zivb Eeig mivb pwavb Tinb huvb Eei myenb. Toq ninb naaig zyruq, ‘yia putq naaiq nxm pcvg haib lovj Eei fai?’+”
8.3: siag Havj Jiaj liud, uaq taub msia'q txn yem fi-li-saa-tia teib puv Rwrnj zyrug mivb lxd huvb tiaj Toq ninb Eei pyauq Zauj livb teig Rwrnj.
8.21: ye-ho-lam zyrug txb Jyenq ninb Eei yetg zuvq Bx'q Jaaj Eei maab Zia mivb Tauj saaj-i uaq. e-Dom Eei pcv weib Jyenq ninb Zauj zaavq Bx'q Jaaj Zia Eei zwavj pcvb pyeiq, mq paag ye-ho-lam Bua luvb mwrnd zang Bx'q Tov weib Jyenq Eei myenb zyrug tu'q pyauj Zwrtq. ninb Eei pcv yaag pyauj Rwrnj pyauq Revg mig a'q.
8.14: haa-saa-en zyrug leib Gxi e-li-saa Rwrnj Tauj ninb Eei zyruq, Ben-haa-Datg, uaq. Ben-haa-Datg naaig ninb, “e-li-saa Navq haiq nx kxvq?” haa-saa-en tau, “ninb Buaj yia, meib Eei pcvg za'kevb haib lovj Eei.”
8.23: ye-ho-lam zruj huvb kunq Eei zyavb hog zevg Fiag Eei sig Zauj ninb zruj Eei yetg zuvq, fiaq Jyenq yu-Daa huvb Eei huvb trub taan.
8.6: huvb tiaj naaig uaq taub msia'q txn Tauj naaiq teij Jauq, uaq taub msia'q txn zyrug kxvq pun ninb mwavj. huvb tiaj zyrug Paaiq taub Jyen Beng ninb Eei sig, kxvq Buaj ninb, “ta'faanb penj naaiq taub msia'q txn Eei yetg zuvq ka'naaiq xij zu'g fuvj Rwrnj pun ninb, lyemb ninb Zwrtq teib puv uaq Nxi Tauj ib zang ninb Eei Dau Zwrtq Eei pwrng xij zu'g fuvj Rwrnj.”
8.2: uaq taub msia'q txn zyrug ei Jyenq Tinb huvb Eei myenb, e-li-saa, Buaj Eei waag zruj. ninb Zauj ninb Eei yetg pyauq myenb Zwrtq mivb yem fi-li-saa-tia teib puv siag Havj.
8.20: ye-ho-lam zruj huvb Eei zyavb hog, e-Dom teig vcvg Jyenq yu-Daa zyrug lyepg ninb Bua kanb Eei huvb.
8.24: ye-ho-lam zyrug kwei seij mig a'q, yaag Zauj ninb Eei ovb Taaij zavj Jyenq Daa-witq Eei zivb. ninb Eei txn, aa-hatg-yaa, zyrug Ripg Jyenq ninb zruj huvb.
8.28: aa-hatg-yaa Zauj aa-hapg Eei txn, yo-lam, Zwrtq mivb Tauj laa-motq-ki-le-aatg Zauj si-lia Eei huvb, haa-saa-en, Bx'q Jaaj. si-lia myenb zruj pun yo-lam zu'g mun.
8.7: e-li-saa mivb Tauj Daa-matq-katg zivb. uaq zang si-lia Eei huvb, Ben-haa-Datg, putq pcvg. maaib myenb kxvq Buaj huvb tiaj, “Tinb huvb Eei myenb taaib Tauj naaiq.”
8.29: yo-lam zyrug Rwrnj Tauj yitq-le-en zxg ninb yem laa-motq Zauj si-lia huvb, haa-saa-en, Bx'q Jaaj zu'g si-lia pcv pun ninb zu'g mun Eei txvj lovj. yu-Daa Eei huvb, ye-ho-lam Eei txn, aa-hatg-yaa, zyrug Fiag Tauj yitq-le-en mavg aa-hapg Eei txn, yo-lam, weig zu'g yo-lam zu'g mun.
8.19: mq paag zyruq weig ninb Eei pru, Daa-witq, maiq myetg yu-Daa, weig zu'g ninb lcvd pun Daa-witq yetg liud maaib zeib fun zruj huvb.
8.17: tovb ninb faauj weig zruj huvb uaq zang, ninb Eei Havb Jeiq tu'q faab zyepg Eeig Havj. ninb yem ye-lu-saa-lem kunq Yetg Havj.
8.27: aa-hatg-yaa ei Jyenq aa-hapg uaq pyauq myenb Eei za'eij zruj. ziuj zyruq mavg ninb zruj waaig sig Navq aa-hapg zruj nx, weig zu'g ninb penj aa-hapg Eei huvb trub Eei yetg taub sia'g laavb.
8.11: Tinb huvb Eei myenb, e-li-saa, nu'g nu'q Eei mavg haa-saa-en Tauj haa-saa-en syavj Eaiq Eei. Tinb huvb Eei myenb yaag Eyemq a'q.
8.5: ke-haa-si kxvq Jyenq Buaj huvb tiaj e-li-saa Navq haiq nx Tevj taig mivb Eei myenb navb taaib uaq zang, tovb ninb Eei txn taig, e-li-saa Tevj navb taaib uaq taub msia'q txn Tauj taaib weig Toq huvb tiaj pun ninb Eei pyauq Zauj livb teig Rwrnj. ke-haa-si kxvq, “yia Eei zyruq, yia Eei huvb aa'b! tovb naaiq taub msia'q txn. naaiq yaag ninb Eei txn, tovb taig mivb e-li-saa Tevj navb taaib uaq taub.”
8.9: haa-saa-en mivb pwavb e-li-saa, yaag lovg feij zyepg taub lxb Txb Tx Jyenq Daa-matq-katg zivb kaub lovj Jiaj Eei ka'naaiq zruj zivb Eeig pun e-li-saa. ninb sruq Jyenq e-li-saa Eei Ra'Myen uaq zang ninb kxvq, “meib Eei pru, si-lia Eei huvb, Ben-haa-Datg, heug yia taaib naaig meib, ‘yia putq naaiq nxm pcvg haib lovj Eei fai?’+”
8.16: i-saa-laa-en Eei huvb, aa-hapg Eei txn, yo-lam, zruj huvb ta'Mmd Havj uaq Havj, ye-ho-saa-fatq Eei txn, ye-ho-lam, faauj weig zruj yu-Daa Eei huvb.
8.4: mivb Toq uaq zang, huvb tiaj Zauj Tinb huvb Eei myenb Eei pru, ke-haa-si, kxvq Jyenq waag. huvb tiaj Buaj ke-haa-si, “Toq meib kxvq e-li-saa zruj yetg zuvq Bua'g hxvb Eei sig pun yia mwavj.”
8.10: e-li-saa tau, “Rwrnj mivb Buaj Ben-haa-Datg, ‘meib za'kevb haib lovj.’ mq paag zyruq, pun yia hiuq tu'q ninb za'kevb xij zu'g taig.”
8.22: e-Dom zyrug vcvg Jyenq yu-Daa Tauj ib Jaaj Nxi. lipq-naa zivb yaag txij uaq teij zyavb hog fib Navq Eei vcvg.
8.12: haa-saa-en naaig kaaj, “tomb kxj aag, meib zruj haiq Euvg Eyemq?” e-li-saa tau, “weig zu'g yia hiuq tu'q meib xij Navq haiq nx zruj hxig i-saa- laa-en myenb. meib xij lovg trud puaq ninb Bua weib Jyenq wrnq Eei txvj, lovg Ru'g Daauq taij ninb Bua Eei myenb lunj myenb, zx'q ninb Bua Eei fu'Jweib faij kwc'q taig, yaag Pi'q Gxi maaib kub vwaad Eei msia'q txn Eei ka'sia.”
8.15: mq paag ta'Eeig Nxi haa-saa-en zx'q Kwaaiq swavj zyemj uam taaib opq Jyenq huvb tiaj Eei Myen. huvb zyrug taig mig a'q. haa-saa-en zyrug Ripg Jyenq zruj si-lia Eei huvb.
8.13: haa-saa-en kxvq, “yia, meib Eei pru, Kuvj Dovg taub Juq Navq. fuvg haib zruj tu'q Zwrtq naaiq teij tomb sig?” e-li-saa tau, “zyruq pun yia hiuq tu'q meib xij tu'q zruj si-lia Eei huvb.”
8.1: e-li-saa kxvq Buaj taub msia'q txn, tovb ninb Eei txn taig, e-li-saa Tevj navb taaib uaq taub, “meib Zauj meib Eei pyauq zov myenb xij zu'g Zwrtq naaiq nxm txvj mivb yem meib kanb yem tu'q Eei txvj, weig zu'g zyruq tivg zyavj pun naaiq nxm teib puv pwavb siag Havj tomb Waav tomb vxg.”
8.26: aa-hatg-yaa tu'q zruj huvb uaq zang ninb Eei Havb Jeiq tu'q Eig zyepg Eeig Havj. ninb yem ye-lu-saa-lem kunq yetg Havj. ninb Eei maa se i-saa-laa-en huvb, om-li Eei sia'g fun, Buaj heug aa-Taa-li-yaa.
8.25: aa-hapg Eei txn, yo-lam, zruj i-saa-laa-en Eei huvb zyepg Eeig Havj uaq Havj, ye-ho-lam Eei txn, aa-hatg-yaa, faauj weig zruj yu-Daa Eei huvb.

3.18: ei zyruq mavg, naaiq se faib fiuq sig. ninb yaag xij zx'q mo-apg myenb Jiu pun yem meib Bua Eei puab Diaq.
3.8: ye-ho-saa-fatq naaig, “yia Bua xij zu'g yavb haiq tiug Jauq mivb Bx'q?” yo-lam tau, “yavb e-Dom Eei teib puvb Waav uaq tiub Jauq mivb.”
3.3: mq paag ninb Zxg paamd zwid Navq zinb Daavg ne-Batg Eei txn, ye-lo-Bo-am, tovb ninb pun i-saa-laa-en myenb paamd zwid. yo-lam yaag maiq Kavq tivb.
3.21: mo-apg Eei zwavj myenb haid kxvq naaiq teij huvb tiaj taaib Zauj ninb Bua Bx'q Jaaj, ta'faanb haib txb tu'q Bx'q Jaaj Eei ua'g king Eei taub taub mJavg txn, maiq kunq koj lunj, tiug Rxib taaib, mivb zuaq Jyenq ninb Bua Eei kapg Jaaij.
3.14: e-li-saa kxvq, “yia zyavq Jyenq zyavb Jyenq Eei zyruq, nrnb Jiaj Eei Tinb huvb, tovb yia fub suj uaq taub lcvd, sij kxvq yia maiq Taaib Zauj meib yem naaiq taub yu-Daa Eei huvb, ye-ho-saa-fatq nx, yia zuvq maiq mavg meib yaag maiq kunq meib a'q.
3.23: ninb Bua kxvq, “oq! naaiq Ryaamq aaq lo'b! Dovg haaij zuvq uaq teij huvb tiaj taij Jaaj a'q. mo-apg myenb aa'b! Bua mivb Zaavq ninb Bua Eei ka'naaiq a'q.”
3.6: yo-lam huvb zyrug yem saa-maa-lia Zwrtq yaag tiug Rxib i-saa-laa-en Eei pcv.
3.2: ei zyruq mavg, yo-lam zruj waaig sig, mq paag maiq Navq ninb Eei tiaj maag zruj Eei, weig zu'g ninb myetg ninb Eei tia zruj taaib zavg Baa-an zyenb Eei la'pyeib tovg.
3.20: ta'Eeig Dxm, leib maiq ko fovg hxg ziag Eei zyavb hog, maaib uam yem e-Dom teig lyrug Jyenq taaib pwavq uaq teij txvj.
3.24: mq paag mo-apg myenb mivb Tauj i-saa-laa-en Eei Zyavq, i-saa-laa-en myenb Zwrtq taaib Bx'q ninb Bua Tauj ninb Bua pyauj. i-saa-laa-en myenb zung Jyenq mivb pia'g ninb Bua Eei teib puv taij mo-apg myenb.
3.7: ninb yaag pun fyenj mivb Buaj yu-Daa Eei huvb, ye-ho-saa-fatq. ninb kxvq, “mo-apg Eei huvb vcvg Jyenq yia. meib Zauj yia mivb Bx'q mo-apg fai?” ye-ho-saa-fatq tau, “yia xij mivb Eei. yia Navq meib nx. yia Eei pc'g fivj yaag Navq meib Eei pc'g fivj, yia Eei maad yaag Navq meib Eei maad.”
3.19: meib Bua xij Bx'q paaig nxmb nxm maaib zivb laatg wrnq Eei zivb Zauj Lo Jiaj Eei nxmb nxm muvq. meib Bua zuvq tu'q kxij ninb Bua tiub tiub lovj Eei Dyavj, yaag zotq Jyenq yetg zuvq uamb zivq, cvj lovg la'pyeiq zruj waaig ninb Bua Eei yetg zuvq kaub lovj Jiaj Eei livb teig.”
3.17: weig zu'g zyruq Navq naaiq nx kxvq, ‘meib Bua maiq tu'q pwatg Ryaauj fai Byuvg mq paag naaiq nxm hxvd xij maaib uam pwavq Revg. meib Bua Zauj meib Bua Eei vovb kwanb, scvb Kuq kwanb, zyrug tu'q hopq.’
3.27: ninb zyrug zx'q ninb Eei txnb Lo, tovb hxpg zu'g Ripg Jyenq ninb zruj huvb uaq taub, yem zivb laatg kub vwaaig fovg hxg puaq ziag. i-saa-laa-en myenb za'kevb! kamb Riaj haig. ninb Bua zyrug Twij Zwrtq zivb cvj Rwrnj ninb Bua kanb Eei teib puv.
3.11: mq paag ye-ho-saa-fatq kxvq, “yem naaiq maiq maaib zyruq Eei trug waag myenb weig pun Bua haib pavg ninb naaig zyruq fai?” i-saa-laa-en huvb Eei yetg taub pcvb pyeiq tau, “saa-fatq Eei txn, e-li-saa, yem naaiq. zinb Daavg ninb fub suj e-li-yaa.”
3.5: mq paag aa-hapg taig liud, mo-apg Eei huvb vcvg Jyenq i-saa-laa-en Eei huvb.
3.9: i-saa-laa-en Eei huvb Zauj yu-Daa Eei huvb Zauj e-Dom Eei huvb zyrug Zwrtq Jauq. ninb Bua Wiv mivb siag Nxi Eei Jauq, zyrug lxd maiq tu'q uam pun pcvb kwanb Zauj scvb Kuq hopq.
3.16: ninb zyrug kxvq, “zyruq Navq naaiq nx kxvq, ‘xij zu'g wetq zwrnj pwavq naaiq nxm hxvd.’
3.4: mo-apg Eei huvb, me-saa, yuvd pa'ki yuvb. Havb Havj ninb xij zu'g fuvj zyepg waang taub pa'ki yuvb Zauj zyepg waang taub pa'ki yuvb kruq Eei pyei mivb pun i-saa-laa-en Eei huvb.
3.10: i-saa-laa-en Eei huvb kxvq, “zu'g Kruq aaq lo'b! zyruq pun yia Bua pua taub huvb kapq zunq weig zx'q yia Bua Jiu pun yem mo-apg myenb Eei puab Diaq fai?”
3.22: luvb Dxm ninb Bua Jiad sin Ryruq Eei pwatg Ba'Nxi ziuj uam. mo-apg myenb mavg mivb pwatg uam si'q Navq Ryaamq nx.
3.12: ye-ho-saa-fatq kxvq, “ninb za'kevb trug zyruq Eei waag.” i-saa-laa-en Eei huvb Zauj ye-ho-saa-fatq Zauj e-Dom Eei huvb zyrug mivb lxd e-li-saa.
3.15: mq paag ib zang txb taub Patq taanb paab Eei myenb taaib yia naaiq.” Patq taanb paab Eei myenb Patq uaq zang, zyruq Eei Qa'q Fiag taaib yem e-li-saa.
3.13: e-li-saa kxvq Buaj i-saa-laa-en Eei huvb, “yia Zauj meib maaib haiq Euvg kwen zu'g? mivb lxd meib Eei tia Zauj meib Eei maa Eei trug waag myenb maa'b!” i-saa-laa-en Eei huvb tiaj tau, “maiq tu'q, weig zu'g se zyruq heug yia Bua pua taub huvb tiaj kapq zunq xij zx'q yia Bua Jiu pun yem mo-apg myenb Eei puab Diaq.”
3.1: ye-ho-saa-fatq zruj yu-Daa Eei huvb zyepg petq Havj uaq Havj, aa-hapg Eei txn, yo-lam, faauj weig zruj i-saa-laa-en Eei huvb. ninb yem saa-maa-lia kunq zyepg Eeig Havj.
3.26: mo-apg Eei huvb pwatg ninb Bx'q maiq hivb winb wavq, ninb zyrug txb Zyetq pc'q taub lovg Ru'g Daauq Eei pcv, xij petq Zwrtq Tauj e-Dom huvb uaq mq paag ninb Bua maiq haib.
3.25: ninb Bua paaig waaig mo-apg myenb Eei zivb. kx'g myenb zx'q la'pyeiq zxi pia'g Rovb Rov lovj Eei livb teig Tauj naaiq teij livb teig Kuvj la'pyeiq pwavq Revg. ninb Bua yaag zotq Dipg nxmb nxm uamb zivq yaag kxij yetg zuvq lovj Eei Dyavj. Kuvj zevg Kin-haa-le-setq Zxg maaib la'pyeiq zivb laatg Navq. lovg Dopg Laav puvj la'pyeiq Eei pcv zyrug weib kxmj Bx'q uaq nxm zivb.

21.18: maa-natq-sej kwei seij mig a'q, yaag zavj Jyenq yem ninb Eei huvb ting Eei Wivj, se utg-saa Eei Wivj. ninb Eei txn, aa-mon, Ripg Jyenq ninb zruj huvb.
21.8: sij kxvq i-saa-laa-en myenb faij fim ei Jyenq yia hatg Eei yetg zuvq waag zruj yaag ei Jyenq yia Eei pru, mo-se, Jiu pun ninb Bua Eei yetg zuvq leib latg, yia zuvq maiq pun ninb Bua zu'g zung Zwrtq.”
21.3: ninb cvj Zeij Jiad tovb ninb Eei tia, he-se-Ki-yaa, paaig waaig uaq teij yem Lav zavg zyenb Eei txvj. ninb cvj weig Baa-an zyenb Zeij ziab txvb, yaag zruj aa-se-laa zyenb Eeid Eei favj, Navq i-saa-laa-en Eei huvb, aa-hapg, nx. ninb paaij yaag zavg luvb zavg Eei Euvb Euvg.
21.21: ninb zwrtg ninb Eei tia Eei yetg zuvq Euvg zeiq zruj. ninb zavg yaag paaij ninb Eei tia zavg Eei miub favj.
21.14: yia xij kwavg yia zevg Fiag Eei myenb, zx'q ninb Bua Jiu pun ninb Bua Eei winb wavq. ninb Bua zyrug zu'g winb wavq luq ninb Bua, Zaavq ninb Bua,
21.23: aa-mon Eei Jyen taaq za'eij vcvg ninb zyrug yem huvb ting ka'Euad taij ninb.
21.6: ninb zx'q ninb kanb Eei txn puaq ziag, yaag zruj faatq, mavg mcvg, kaanq hei, Bruq kwaaj. ziuj zyruq mavg ninb zruj waaig sig Zamq haig, Zua'q zyruq Qiaj Jiad haig.
21.2: ziuj zyruq mavg ninb zruj waaig sig. ninb ei Jyenq zyruq zung Zwrtq i-saa-laa-en myenb Eei uaq Daavg mcvj uaq teij fivb fivj myenb zruj kamb Riaq haig Eei sig.
21.20: ziuj zyruq mavg, aa-mon zruj waaig sig Navq ninb Eei tia, maa-natq-sej, zruj nx.
21.24: mq paag yu-Daa teib puv Eei pc'g fivj taij tovb taaq za'eij taij huvb tiaj uaq teij myenb. ninb Bua yaag lyepg aa-mon Eei txn, yo-si-yaa, tiq ninb zruj huvb.
21.7: ninb zx'q ninb zu'g taaib uaq nxm aa-se-laa zyenb Eeid Eei favj an Jyenq zavg zyruq Eei pyauq ka'Euad. se naaiq nxm pyauq zyruq kxvq Buaj Daa-witq Zauj ninb Eei txn, saa-lo-mxn, “se naaiq nxm pyauq Zauj ye-lu-saa-lem zivb yia yem fivb fivj i-saa-laa-en myenb Bu'Dovj kinq Zwrtq taaib lyepg yia kanb Eei mevb weig yetg liud.
21.19: aa-mon faauj weig zruj huvb uaq zang, ninb Eei Havb Jeiq tu'q Eig zyepg Eeig Havj. ninb yem ye-lu-saa-lem kunq i Havj. ninb Eei maa Eei Buaj heug me-sun-le-metq. se yotq-Baa myenb, haa-lutq, Eei sia'q.
21.17: maa-natq-sej kunq Eei zyavb hog zruj liud zevg Fiag Eei sig, Zauj ninb zruj Eei yetg zuvq, Zauj ninb paamd Eei zwid, fiaq Jyenq yu-Daa huvb Eei huvb trub taan.
21.11: “yu-Daa Eei huvb, maa-natq-sej, zruj naaiq teij kamb Riaq haig, yruj haig Eei sig. ninb zruj kaub waaig yem Daavg ninb uaq teij aa-mo-lai myenb. ninb lovg ninb Eei miub favj pun yu-Daa myenb paamd zwid Zamq haig.
21.5: ninb yem zavg zyruq Eei pyauq i nxm laatg ka'Euad Eei txvj weig luvb zavg Eei Euvb Euvg Zeij ziab txvb.
21.9: mq paag ninb Bua maiq mwavj. maa-natq-sej pcv ninb Bua zruj waaig sig kaub Zamq zyruq yem i-saa-laa-en myenb Eei uaq Daavg mcvj myetg uaq teij fivb fivj myenb.
21.16: maiq taan Bua'g naaiq. maa-natq-sej taij Kuq myenb, pun Ryaamq lyrug Zwrtq Zamq, zuvq pwavq ye-lu-saa-lem yem naaiq puv mivb Tauj uaq puv. Zwrtq liud naaiq, ninb pun yu-Daa myenb paamd zwid, ziuj zyruq mavg ninb Bua zyrug zruj waaig sig.
21.4: ninb yem zavg zyruq Eei pyauq Zeij ziab txvb, se yem zyruq kxvq, “yia xij lyepg yia Eei mevb yem ye-lu-saa-lem,” uaq nxm txvj.
21.10: zyruq lovg ninb Eei pru, trug waag myenb, kxvq,
21.22: ninb kwavg zyruq, ninb Eei Eei ovb Taaij Eei Tinb huvb, maiq yavb zyruq Eei Jauq.
21.12: weig naaiq, zyruq, i-saa-laa-en myenb Eei Tinb huvb, kxvq, ‘yia xij pun ye-lu-saa-lem Zauj yu-Daa zu'g tomb ze'g naang. haiq taub haid naaiq teij sig, mnxmb zyrug Givj Revg uaq.
21.15: weig zu'g ei yia mavg, ninb Bua zruj waaig sig yem ninb Bua Eei ovb Taaij Zwrtq i-yipq Tauj ib Nxi.’+”
21.13: yia xij tivg ye-lu-saa-lem Eei zwid Navq yia tivg saa-maa-lia Eei zwid nx, yaag Navq yia tivg aa-hapg Eei zeib fun Eei zwid. yia xij sxtq ye-lu-saa-lem Navq myenb sxtq yenq nx. sxtq liud cvj Gopq Jyenq.
21.1: maa-natq-sej faauj weig zruj huvb uaq zang, ninb tu'q zyepg Eeig Havj. ninb yem ye-lu-saa-lem kunq Mmd zyepg Mmd Havj. ninb Eei maa Eei Buaj heug hepq-si-Baa.
21.26: ninb zavj Jyenq utg-saa Eei Wivj, ninb kanb Eei zruq. ninb Eei txn, yo-si-yaa, Ripg Jyenq ninb zruj huvb.
21.25: aa-mon kunq Eei zyavb hog zruj liud zevg Fiag Eei sig fiaq Jyenq yu-Daa huvb Eei huvb trub taan.

14.18: aa-maa-si-yaa zruj zevg Fiag Eei sig fiaq Jyenq yu-Daa huvb Eei huvb trub taan.
14.8: aa-maa-si-yaa Paaiq trug fyenj myenb mivb lxd ye-hu Eei fun, ye-ho-aa-haatg Eei txn, i-saa-laa-en myenb Eei huvb, ye-ho-aatg, kxvq Buaj ninb, “taaib maa'b! Bua i taub Myen txij Myen Bx'q Jaaj.”
14.3: ziuj zyruq mavg, aa-maa-si-yaa zruj tu'q hxpg mq paag maiq Navq ninb Eei ovb Taaij, Daa-witq, zruj Eei. ninb ei ninb Eei tia, yo-aatg, Eei Euvg zeiq zruj Euvb Euvg.
14.21: yu-Daa Eei zwavj pc'g fivj lyepg aa-saa-li-yaa Ripg Jyenq zruj huvb tiq ninb Eei tia, aa-maa-si-yaa. uaq zang aa-saa-li-yaa tu'q zyepg lua'g Havj.
14.14: ninb zx'q Revg yem zavg zyruq Eei pyauq ka'Euad Zauj yem huvb ting syru Jaaij Eei ka'naaiq Eei txvj Eei Jyem Eaanb Zauj Jaab txvj. ninb yaag zx'q teij myenb mivb zruj txvb taaub zyrug Rwrnj saa-maa-lia zivb mig a'q.
14.23: yo-aatg Eei txn, aa-maa-si-yaa, zruj yu-Daa Eei huvb zyepg Mmd Havj uaq Havj, ye-ho-aatg Eei txn, ye-lo-Bo-am, yem saa-maa-lia faauj weig zruj i-saa-laa-en Eei huvb yaag kunq feij zyepg yetq Havj.
14.6: mq paag ninb maiq taij tovb taij ninb Eei tia uaq teij Jyen Eei txn ziuj fiaq Jyenq mo-se Eei leib latg sru. zyruq hatg Eei waag kxvq, “maiq tuvq weig txnb Jweiq zruj Eei zwid taij tiaj maag. yaag maiq tuvq weig tiaj maag zruj Eei zwid taij txnb Jweiq. kx'g myenb xij zu'g weig kx'g myenb Eei zwid zu'g taig.”
14.2: aa-maa-si-yaa zruj huvb uaq zang, ninb Eei Havb Jeiq tu'q Eig zyepg Mmd Havj. ninb yem ye-lu-saa-lem kunq Eig zyepg Juaq Havj. ninb Eei maa Eei Buaj heug ye-ho-atg-Din, se ye-lu-saa-lem zivb Eei myenb.
14.20: ninb Bua lovg maad Tx ninb Eei sei Rwrnj ye-lu-saa-lem, Zauj ninb Eei ovb Taaij zavj Jyenq yem Daa-witq Eei zivb.
14.24: ei zyruq mavg ninb zruj waaig sig, maiq kwavg ne-Batg Eei txn, ye-lo-Bo-am, zruj Eei yetg zuvq zwid, tovb ninb pun i-saa-laa-en myenb paamd Eei zwid.
14.28: ye-lo-Bo-am zruj zevg Fiag Eei sig, Zauj ninb zruj Eei yetg zuvq, Zauj ninb Eei Qa'q, ninb Navq haiq nx Bx'q Jaaj, Navq haiq nx tu'q tovb zinb Daavg penj yu-Daa Eei Daa-matq-katg zivb Zauj haa-matq zivb Rwrnj taaib penj i-saa-laa-en Eei, naaiq teij yetg zuvq sig, fiaq Jyenq i-saa-laa-en huvb Eei huvb trub taan.
14.7: aa-maa-si-yaa yem Raub hxvd taij taig yetg waang taub e-Dom myenb, yaag Bx'q hivb zx'q tu'q se-e-laa zivb, cvj Tiuq zivb Eei Buaj heug yokq-Te-en. naaiq nxm zivb Zxg Navq naaiq nx heug Tauj ib Jaaj Nxi.
14.29: ye-lo-Bo-am kwei seij mig a'q, ninb Eei txn, sej-Kaa-li-yaa, Ripg Jyenq ninb zruj huvb.
14.19: yem ye-lu-saa-lem maaib myenb peig Diaq Zaavb laavb xij vcvg aa-maa-si-yaa, ninb zyrug pyauj mivb laa-Kitq zivb, mq paag ninb Bua Paaiq myenb mivb Tauj laa-Kitq, yem uaq taij ninb.
14.17: i-saa-laa-en Eei huvb, ye-ho-aa-haatg, Eei txn, ye-ho-aatg, kwei seij liud, yu-Daa Eei huvb, yo-aatg Eei txn, aa-maa-si-yaa, Zxg zyavb Jyenq zyepg Mmd Havj.
14.27: zyruq yaag maiq kxvq ninb xij zx'q i-saa-laa-en Eei Buaj yem luvb Diaq sxtq kwavg, ninb zyrug lovg ye-ho-aatg Eei txn, ye-lo-Bo-am, Fruj ninb Bua.
14.11: mq paag aa-maa-si-yaa maiq mwavj naaiq teij waag. i-saa-laa-en Eei huvb, ye-ho-aatg, zyrug taaib yem yu-Daa teig Eei Betg-se-metq muvq, Zauj yu-Daa Eei huvb, aa-maa-si-yaa, txij Myen Bx'q Jaaj.
14.5: zruj kau, aa-maa-si-yaa yetq tu'q kunq kua'q wrnq Eei, ninb zyrug zx'q tovb zinb Daavg taij ninb Eei tia uaq teij Jyen, taij Revg mig a'q.
14.9: mq paag i-saa-laa-en Eei huvb, ye-ho-aatg, cvj Paaiq trug fyenj myenb mivb Buaj yu-Daa Eei huvb, aa-maa-si-yaa, “maaib zuvb Fimq yem le-Baa-nxn Bov pun waag mivb Buaj tiub yem le-Baa-nxn Bov Eei sij-Daa zovb Dyavj, ‘puvj meib Eei sia'q pun yia Eei txn lovg zruj auq.’ Ga'haaq maaib taub Yiab zxib Jiaj Jauq Zaaiq waaig uaq zuvb Fimq.
14.16: ye-ho-aatg kwei seij mig a'q, yaag Zauj i-saa-laa-en Eei huvb zavj Jyenq saa-maa-lia. ninb Eei txn, ye-lo-Bo-am, cvj Ripg Jyenq ninb zruj huvb.
14.4: mq paag ninb maiq Zc'q yem Lav zavg zyenb Eei txvj. pc'g fivj Zxg yem uaq fovg hxg ziag yaag puaq huv.
14.10: meib za'kevb Bx'q hivb e-Dom myenb mig a'q. ib zang meib zyrug Zevb Lo a'q. xij zu'g pwavq Hruq meib tu'q taaib Eei Favb laavg yaag yem Jyenq pyauq maa'b! weig haiq tiug Jiad Hruq Zua'q sig pun meib kanb Zauj yu-Daa teig yetg zuvq zu'g paaig?”
14.22: aa-maa-si-yaa kwei seij mig a'q. Ga'haaq aa-saa-li-yaa tu'q Zeij Jiad e-latq zivb cvj fuvj Rwrnj pun yu-Daa.
14.12: yu-Daa zyrug swei i-saa-laa-en. kx'g myenb pyauj Jyenq Rwrnj kx'g myenb Eei pyauq.
14.15: ye-ho-aatg zruj zevg Fiag Eei sig Zauj ninb Eei Qa'q, lyemb ninb Zauj yu-Daa Eei huvb, aa-maa-si-yaa, Bx'q Jaaj Eei sig, fiaq Jyenq i-saa-laa-en huvb Eei huvb trub taan.
14.13: yem Betg-se-metq muvq, i-saa-laa-en Eei huvb, ye-ho-aatg, zx'q aa-hatg-yaa Eei fun, yo-aatg Eei txn, yu-Daa Eei huvb, aa-maa-si-yaa. Ga'haaq ye-ho-aatg mivb ye-lu-saa-lem Zc'q waaig zivb laatg yem e-faa-im laatg kcvb mivb Tauj kx'q kcvb, Daau feij pc'q Dx'g.
14.1: ye-ho-aa-haatg Eei txn, ye-ho-aatg, zruj i-saa-laa-en Eei huvb i Havj uaq Havj, yo-aatg Eei txn, aa-maa-si-yaa, faauj weig zruj yu-Daa Eei huvb.
14.26: weig zu'g zyruq mavg pwatg i-saa-laa-en Eei zwavj myenb, maiq kunq zruj nrub fai maiq zruj nrub Eei, zu'g syrug Kruq yaag maiq maaib haiq taub Tevj.
14.25: se tovb naaiq taub huvb cvj Bx'q tu'q teib puv Rwrnj, pun i-saa-laa-en Eei kapg Jaaij yem le-Bo-haa-matq mivb Tauj aa-laa-Baa Eei Kxiq, Navq zyruq, i-saa-laa-en Eei Tinb huvb, lovg ninb Eei pru, se yem katg-he-fe Eei trug waag myenb, aa-mitq-Tai Eei txn, yo-naa, kxvq Eei waag.

23.18: huvb tiaj kxvq, “sweib ninb yem naaig a'q. maiq tuvq pun haiq taub swiq ninb Eei Buvq.” ninb Bua zyrug lyrub ninb Eei Buvq Zauj yem saa-maa-lia taaib uaq taub trug waag myenb Eei Buvq.

2.3: maaib kwanb yem Betg-en Eei trug waag myenb Zwrtq taaib pwavb e-li-saa naaig kaaj, “meib hiuq Eei fai? ib Nxi zyruq xij txb meib Eei saib tiaj leib Gxi meib a'q.” e-li-saa tau, “yia hiuq Eei, mq paag maiq tuvq kxvq.”
2.21: ninb zyrug Zwrtq mivb Tauj uamb zivq uaq cvj zx'q naaiq teij Rauq toj Jyenq uam ka'Euad yaag kxvq, “zyruq Navq naaiq nx kxvq, ‘yia pun naaiq teij uam lovj mig a'q. yavb naaiq Jiaj naaiq teij uam maiq hxig myenb taig fai pun myenb waaig kub vwaad.’+”
2.14: ninb lovg yem e-li-yaa Eei sin Dxtq Fiag taaib Eei tomb lwib Daauq Bx'q uam yaag kxvq, “zyruq, e-li-yaa Eei Tinb huvb, yem haaij?” Bx'q uam uaq zang, uam zyrug pun Gxi zaaij mcvj Byaaug mcvj. e-li-saa zyrug Jiaj Daaib mig a'q.
2.23: e-li-saa yem ye-li-Ko Zwrtq Jauq mivb Betg-en. yem Jauq zavg uaq zang maaib teij txn yem zivb Zwrtq taaib Jyetq ninb. ninb Bua kxvq, “ovb mGxvb Fav, faauj mivb maa'b! ov mGxvb Fav, faauj mivb maa'b!”
2.6: e-li-yaa kxvq Buaj e-li-saa, “meib yem naaiq zuaq og. zyruq Paaiq yia mivb Jx-Dcn Daaib.” mq paag e-li-saa kxvq, “yia zyavq Jyenq zyavb Jyenq Eei zyruq yaag zyavq Jyenq meib Eei mcvg lcvd, yia maiq leib Gxi meib.” ninb Bua i taub cvj kan Jyenq Jauq mivb a'q.
2.2: e-li-yaa kxvq Buaj e-li-saa, “meib yem naaiq zuaq og. zyruq Paaiq yia mivb Betg-en.” mq paag e-li-saa kxvq, “yia zyavq Jyenq zyavb Jyenq Eei zyruq yaag zyavq Jyenq meib Eei mcvg lcvd, yia maiq leib Gxi meib.” ninb Bua zyrug mivb Betg-en.
2.20: e-li-saa kxvq, “zx'q nxm syavb Rxmg taaib tapq Jyenq Rauq pun yia.” ninb Bua zyrug txb taaib pun ninb.
2.24: e-li-saa Win Rwrnj mavg ninb Bua yaag tevq zyruq Eei Buaj zyruj ninb Bua. maaib i taub Jyepg Eeid yem lomg Zwrtq taaib petq feij zyepg Eeig taub naaiq teij txn.
2.7: maaib Mmd zyepg taub trug waag myenb kan Jyenq ninb Bua mivb yaag sruq Jyenq ko teij Eei Win mivb e-li-yaa Zauj e-li-saa tivb Jyenq Jx-Dcn Daaib Len uaq nxm txvj.
2.19: maaib teij yem zivb Eei myenb kxvq Buaj e-li-saa, “yia Bua Eei tomb kxj aag, meib pwatg yia Bua Eei zivb Eei txvb taaub lovj Eei, mq paag uam maiq penj. msia'q txn Kuvj waaig kub vwaad Navq.”
2.17: mq paag ninb Bua Qa'q Toq pun ninb Bua mivb, Tauj e-li-saa syavj Eaiq Eei. ninb zyrug kxvq, “Paaiq ninb Bua mivb maa'b!” ninb Bua zyrug Paaiq Mmd zyepg taub myenb mivb lxd pua Nxi yaag lxd maiq pwatg ninb.
2.11: ninb Bua i taub yetg ping mivb yetg ping kxvq waag uaq zang, lyemb zeib maaib trud Eei Zia Zauj maaib trud Eei maad hing Zwrtq taaib zx'q ninb Bua i taub pun Gxi. e-li-yaa zyrug yem Ryaaub zung faauj luvb mig a'q.
2.5: maaib kwanb yem ye-li-Ko Eei trug waag myenb mivb Tauj e-li-saa uaq naaig ninb, “meib hiuq Eei fai? ib Nxi zyruq xij txb meib Eei saib tiaj leib Gxi meib mivb mig a'q.” e-li-saa tau, “yia hiuq Eei, mq paag maiq tuvq kxvq a'q.”
2.9: Jiaj uaq vaang zi'g Daaib liud, e-li-yaa kxvq Buaj e-li-saa, “zyruq maiq kcvb zipq yia leib Gxi meib, meib xij yia weig meib zruj haiq Euvg kunq Toq a'q.” e-li-saa tau, “Toq pun yia tu'q Ripg suvb kruq meib Eei Qa'q.”
2.16: ninb Bua kxvq, “mavg maa'b! yia Bua, meib Eei pru, maaib Mmd zyepg taub henq Eei mJavg txn. Toq pun ninb Bua mivb lxd meib Eei saib tiaj. Riaj zyruq Eei sivj livb zx'q ninb mivb cvj puvj ninb Fiag haiq nxm Bov kub vwaaig fai haiq nxm hxvd.” e-li-saa tau, “maiq tuvq Paaiq ninb Bua mivb.”
2.4: e-li-yaa kxvq Buaj e-li-saa, “meib yem naaiq zuaq og. zyruq Paaiq yia mivb ye-li-Ko.” mq paag e-li-saa kxvq, “yia zyavq Jyenq zyavb Jyenq Eei zyruq yaag zyavq Jyenq meib lcvd, yia maiq leib Gxi meib.” ninb Bua zyrug mivb ye-li-Ko.
2.10: e-li-yaa kxvq, “meib Toq Eei se a'g haig, mq paag zyruq zipq yia leib Gxi meib mivb Eei zyavb hog, sij kxvq meib pwatg yia, meib zyrug tu'q a'q. mq paag sij kxvq meib maiq pwatg yia, meib zyrug maiq tu'q zipq.”
2.22: yem naaig taaib, uam zyrug lovj Tauj ib Jaaj Nxi, ziuj e-li-saa kxvq Eei waag.
2.12: e-li-saa pwatg zyrug heug Zwrtq kxvq, “yia Eei tia aa'b! yia Eei tia! i-saa-laa-en Eei Bx'q Jaaj Zia Zauj keb maad pcv aa'b!” Ga'haaq e-li-saa maiq tu'q pwatg e-li-yaa a'q. e-li-saa zyrug zx'q ninb kanb Eei lwi petq zruj i mcvj.
2.15: yem ye-li-Ko taaib uaq kwanb trug waag myenb mavg Jyenq zyrug kxvq, “e-li-saa tu'q e-li-yaa Eei Qa'q mig a'q.” ninb Bua zyrug mivb zipq ninb yaag yem ninb Eei Ra'Myen Baapq Fiag Tauj Dau.
2.13: e-li-saa zx'q yem e-li-yaa Dxtq Fiag taaib Eei tomb lwi zyrug Rwrnj mivb sruq Jyenq Jx-Dcn Daaib Len.
2.1: Tauj zyavb hog zyruq xij lovg Ryaaub zung txb e-li-yaa faauj luvb, e-li-yaa Zauj e-li-saa yem kin-kaan Zwrtq Jauq mivb.
2.25: e-li-saa yem naaig mivb Tauj Kaan-men Bov, Ga'haaq cvj Rwrnj Tauj saa-maa-lia.

20.18: ‘maaib teij yem meib kanb Eei Ryaamb fei Zwrtq Eei txnb Jweiq funb fa'q zuvq xij zu'g kwaatq mivb yem Baa-Bi-lon Eei huvb ting penj zu'g im toq Eei myenb.’+”
20.3: “o zyruq aag, Toq meib Javj Jyenq yia yem meib Eei Ra'Myen zyepg zua'q Eei kan lovj meib yaag ziuj meib mavg yia zruj tu'q lovj.” he-se-Ki-yaa zyrug Eyemq tu'q Hruq mun haig.
20.8: he-se-Ki-yaa naaig i-saa-yaa, “maaib haiq Euvg Javb hog pun Ziv zyruq xij zxg yia lovj, Tauj ta'faam Nxi yia tu'q mivb zavg zyruq Eei pyauq?”
20.19: he-se-Ki-yaa tau i-saa-yaa, “meib trug taaib naaiq Jruj zyruq Eei waag se lovj Eei.” ninb Navq naaiq nx kxvq weig zu'g ninb yem Hruq Namq, “ta'faanb yia Eei seij zeiq Taaib pcvb Eei, maiq maaib sig maiq zeid?”
20.9: i-saa-yaa tau, “naaiq se zyruq xij pun meib Eei Javb hog weig pun Ziv zyruq xij ei Jyenq ninb lcvd Eei waag zruj. meib xij tovb linb mivb uaq Daavg zyepg wrng Tei fai xij tovb linb Rwrnj Ga'haaq Gaav zyepg wrng Tei?”
20.7: i-saa-yaa kxvq, “zx'q teij vovb Exj pyruq taaib.” myenb zyrug zx'q taaib opq he-se-Ki-yaa Eei zweib. ninb zyrug lovj mig a'q.
20.5: “xij zu'g Rwrnj mivb Buaj yia Eei pc'g fivj Eei pyeiq zeiq, he-se-Ki-yaa, ‘zyruq, meib Eei ovb Taaij, Daa-witq, Eei Tinb huvb, Navq naaiq nx kxvq, “yia haid meib tauj kauj Eei waag yaag pwatg meib Eei uamb mweig. yia xij zxg lovj meib. cvj Jiaj mivb Tauj ta'faam Nxi meib tu'q mivb pia'g zavg zyruq Eei pyauq.
20.16: i-saa-yaa kxvq Buaj he-se-Ki-yaa, “mwavj zyruq Eei waag maa'b!
20.20: he-se-Ki-yaa kunq Eei zyavb hog zruj liud zevg Fiag Eei sig, Zauj ninb Eei Qa'q zruj Eei yetg zuvq, Zauj ninb wetq uamb tomb, wetq uamb Jauq kan Daub Diaq mivb puvj uam pia'g zivb ka'Euad naaiq teij yetg zuvq sig, fiaq Jyenq yu-Daa huvb Eei huvb trub taan.
20.17: ‘Nxib Eia'g zuvq xij Tauj. yem meib Eei huvb ting Eei yetg zuvq ka'naaiq Zauj meib Eei ovb Taaij syru Tauj ib Jaaj Nxi Eei ka'naaiq, xij zu'g Zaavq mivb Tauj Baa-Bi-lon. yetg Euvg yaag maiq lyrub.’ naaiq se zyruq kxvq Eei waag.
20.14: trug waag myenb, i-saa-yaa, naaig kaaj, “naaiq teij myenb kxvq haiq Euvg? yem haaij taaib?” he-se-Ki-yaa tau, “ninb Bua yem ko Eei teib puv taaib, se yem Baa-Bi-lon taaib.”
20.4: i-saa-yaa maiq kcvb tu'q Zwrtq huvb ting Bu'Dovj uaq Kav Tiv uaq zang, zyruq kxvq Buaj ninb,
20.21: he-se-Ki-yaa kwei seij mig a'q, ninb Eei txn, maa-natq-sej, Ripg Jyenq ninb zruj huvb.
20.2: he-se-Ki-yaa zyrug Win Myen mivb Fovg uaq puv tauj kauj kxvq Buaj zyruq,
20.6: yia cvj xij Jaa pun meib zyavb zyepg Mmd Havj yaag xij Fruj naaiq nxm zivb leib Dutq atg-si-lia huvb Eei puab Diaq. weig yia Eei pru, Daa-witq, yia xij peu naaiq nxm zivb.”+’+”
20.13: he-se-Ki-yaa zipq naaiq teij trug fyenj myenb yaag pun ninb Bua mavg ninb syru Jaaij Eei ka'naaiq Eei txvj yetg zuvq ka'naaiq. se pun ninb Bua mavg Jyem, Eaanb, laapg liug, Jaaij haig Eei yrub Zauj ninb Bx'q Jaaj Eei ua'g king, tovb ninb maaib Eei Euvb Euvg Jaaij Eei ka'naaiq. yem ninb Eei huvb ting Zauj zyavb nxm kua'q Eei ka'naaiq. maiq maaib yetg Euvg he-se-Ki-yaa maiq pun ninb Bua pwatg.
20.12: txij uaq teij zyavb hog, Baa-laa-Dan Eei txn, Baa-Bi-lon kua'q Eei huvb, me-lo-Dakg-Baa-laa-Dan, haid kxvq he-se-Ki-yaa putq pcvg zyrug fuvj fyenj Zauj zivb Eeig mivb pun ninb.
20.15: i-saa-yaa naaig, “yem meib Eei huvb ting ninb Bua tu'q pwatg haiq Euvg?” he-se-Ki-yaa kxvq, “yem yia Eei huvb ting ninb Bua tu'q pwatg Euvb Euvg. yia Jaaij Eei ka'naaiq maiq maaib yetg Euvg yia maiq pun ninb Bua mavg.”
20.11: trug waag myenb, i-saa-yaa, zyrug Toq zyruq.  zyruq zyrug pun tovb linb yem aa-hatg Eei Tei Twij Rwrnj ninb Jiaj Daavg Eei zyepg wrng Tei.
20.1: txij uaq teij zyavb hog he-se-Ki-yaa putq pcvg Kruq, Kaaq teij taig mig a'q. aa-mxtq Eei txn, uaq taub trug waag myenb, i-saa-yaa, mivb mavg ninb cvj kxvq Buaj ninb, “zyruq Navq naaiq kxvq, ‘meib xij zu'g liug leid Euvb Euvg suv weig zu'g meib zuvq xij zu'g taig. meib maiq haib lovj.’+”
20.10: he-se-Ki-yaa tau, “tovb linb mivb uaq Daavg zyepg wrng se kaub heg. yia kaub xij tovb linb Rwrnj Ga'haaq zyepg wrng.”

24.18: sej-De-Ki-yaa faauj weig zruj huvb uaq zang, ninb tu'q Eig zyepg yetq Havj. ninb yem ye-lu-saa-lem kunq zyepg yetq Havj. ninb Eei maa Eei Buaj heug haa-mu-Taan, se lipq-naa myenb, ye-le-mi, Eei sia'q.
24.3: naaiq teij sig Zwrtq taaib ziuj zyruq hatg Eei waag weig pun yu-Daa myenb maiq tu'q yem ninb Eei Ra'Myen. se laaij maa-natq-sej zruj Eei yetg zuvq zwid,
24.8: ye-ho-yaa-Kin faauj weig zruj huvb uaq zang, ninb tu'q zyepg petq Havj. ninb yem ye-lu-saa-lem kunq pua Laaj Eia'g. ninb Eei maa Eei Buaj heug ne-hutg-Taa, se ye-lu-saa-lem myenb, en-naa-Tan, Eei sia'q.
24.19: ziuj zyruq mavg, sej-De-Ki-yaa zruj waaig sig, Navq ye-ho-yaa-Kin zruj nx.
24.9: ziuj zyruq mavg, ye-ho-yaa-Kin zruj waaig sig Navq ninb Eei tia zruj nx.
24.7: i-yipq Eei huvb maiq cvj Zwrtq ninb Eei kua'q, weig zu'g Baa-Bi-lon Eei huvb zx'q Revg ninb Eei teib puv mig a'q, yem i-yipq Do'q mivb Tauj yu-fe-titg Daaib.
24.5: ye-ho-yaa-Kim kunq Eei zyavb hog zruj liud zevg Fiag Eei sig Zauj ninb zruj Eei yetg zuvq, fiaq Jyenq yu-Daa huvb Eei huvb trub taan.
24.16: Baa-Bi-lon Eei huvb yaag kwaatq yetg zuvq haib Bx'q Jaaj henq Eei pcv siag Zin taub, yaag kwaatq puab taub lovj Eei zavg myenb Zauj Lia'g zavg yetg Zin taub mivb Baa-Bi-lon. yetg zuvq henq Eei, Pwij tu'q zruj pcv Bx'q Jaaj Eei myenb.
24.20: se laaij zyruq Qiaj Jiad haig, ye-lu-saa-lem Zauj yu-Daa Zivj zu'g naaiq teij sig Tauj zyruq kwavg, maiq pun ninb Bua yem ninb Eei Ra'Myen. zruj kau, sej-De-Ki-yaa vcvg Jyenq Baa-Bi-lon Eei huvb.
24.17: Baa-Bi-lon Eei huvb lyepg ye-ho-yaa-Kin Eei yrub tiaj, matq-Taa-ni-yaa, zruj huvb tiq ye-ho-yaa-Kin, cvj Tiuq matq-Taa-ni-yaa Eei Buaj heug sej-De-Ki-yaa.
24.14: ninb cvj kwaatq Revg ye-lu-saa-lem Eei pc'g fivj, Zauj yetg zuvq pcvb pyeiq Zauj henq haig Eei pcv, lyemb yetg zuvq puab taub lovj Eei zavg myenb Zauj Dyavb zavg. yetg zuvq maaib yetg waang taub. Kuvj zevg kaub Jomg Jiaj Eei myenb tu'q yem teib puv Navq.
24.4: yaag laaij ninb taij Kuq myenb Zamq, pun Ryaamq lyrug Zwrtq pwavq ye-lu-saa-lem. zyruq yaag maiq kwavg pun ninb.
24.2: zyruq pun Baa-Bi-lon myenb, si-lia myenb, mo-apg myenb Zauj am-mon myenb Eei yetg kwanb yetg kwanb za'g pcv taaib Bx'q ninb. ninb Paaiq ninb Bua taaib weig xij myetg yu-Daa ziuj zyruq lovg ninb Eei pru, zwavj trug waag myenb, kxvq Eei waag.
24.6: ye-ho-yaa-Kim zyrug kwei seij mig a'q. ninb Eei txn, ye-ho-yaa-Kin, yaag Ripg Jyenq ninb zruj huvb.
24.13: Navq zyruq kxvq nx, ne-Bu-Katq-netq-saa zx'q Revg yem zavg zyruq Eei pyauq Zauj yem huvb ting Eei yetg zuvq Jaaij Eei ka'naaiq. ninb yaag zx'q i-saa-laa-en Eei huvb, saa-lo-mxn, weig zavg zyruq Eei pyauq zruj taaib Eei Jyemb Jaab txvj Va'q penj yetg Levj yetg Levj.
24.12: yu-Daa Eei huvb, ye-ho-yaa-Kin, Zauj ninb Eei maa, ninb Eei Jyen, ninb Eei zruj Lo Eei myenb Zauj yem huvb ting Eei Jyen yetg zuvq Eyemg swei pun ninb. Baa-Bi-lon Eei huvb zruj huvb ta'petq Havj uaq Havj, ninb txb ye-ho-yaa-Kin mivb wrnj Jyenq.
24.15: ne-Bu-Katq-netq-saa kwaatq ye-ho-yaa-Kin mivb Baa-Bi-lon. lyemb huvb maag Zauj ninb Eei auq Bua, ninb Eei Jyen Zauj uaq nxm teib puv zruj Lo Eei myenb, ne-Bu-Katq-netq-saa yem ye-lu-saa-lem kwaatq mivb Baa-Bi-lon Revg.
24.11: pcvb pyeiq weib Jyenq zivb uaq zang, Baa-Bi-lon Eei huvb, ne-Bu-Katq-netq-saa, mivb Tauj ye-lu-saa-lem.
24.1: yem ye-ho-yaa-Kim kunq Eei zyavb hog, Baa-Bi-lon Eei huvb, ne-Bu-Katq-netq-saa, pia'g taaib Zaavq yu-Daa teib puv. ye-ho-yaa-Kim yaag zu'g yem ninb Eei puab Diaq Bua'g ninb kunq pua Havj. Ga'haaq ninb vcvg, maiq mwavj ne-Bu-Katq-netq-saa.
24.10: uaq zang Baa-Bi-lon Eei huvb, ne-Bu-Katq-netq-saa, Eei pcvb pyeiq taaib weib kxmj ye-lu-saa-lem.

7.18: sig Zwrtq taaib Navq Tinb huvb Eei myenb kxvq Buaj huvb tiaj. ninb kxvq, “Fav Nxi leib maiq ko naaiq nxm zyavb hog, yem saa-maa-lia Eei zivb kcvb, siag mx'q Byaub maaig tu'q Eig zinb levb Eaanb. zyepg Mmd mx'q Byaub Baa-li yaag maaig tu'q Eig zinb levb Eaanb.”
7.3: yem zivb kcvb Daavg maaib pyei taub putq komb huq pcvg Eei myenb. ninb Bua laanb kxvq Buaj laanb, “Bua weig haiq tiug zweid Jyenq naaiq zuaq taig?
7.8: uaq teij putq komb huq pcvg Eei myenb mivb Tauj Zyavq ka'Len pia'g nxm Dopg liub. ninb Bua yrug Eang yrug hopq, cvj zx'q Jyem Eaanb Zauj lwib hruj txb mivb pivj Jyenq. ninb Bua cvj Rwrnj taaib pia'g kanb nxm Dopg liub, zx'q yem uaq nxm Eei ka'naaiq fib Navq Eei txb mivb pivj.
7.19: uaq taub pcvb pyeiq zinb Daavg kxvq Buaj Tinb huvb Eei myenb “mavg maa'b! maiq kunq zyruq pun luvb kcvb Gxi Revg, zuvq maiq haib maaib naaiq Euvg sig saa'b?” Tinb huvb Eei myenb tau, “meib kanb Eei mziv tu'q pwatg mq paag meib maiq tu'q Eang yetg teij.”
7.9: Ga'haaq ninb Bua laanb kxvq Buaj laanb, “Bua Navq naaiq zruj se maiq hxpg. ib Nxi maaib Kuq fyenj. sij kxvq Bua maiq Buaj myenb cvj zuaq Tauj luvb Fav, zwid zyrug Dxtq zu'g Bua a'q. taaib maa'b! Bua ib zang mivb Buaj huvb tiaj Eei Jyen.”
7.7: Ryemb yaavb Eei zyavb hog ninb Bua zyrug pyauj, kwavg Jyenq ninb Bua Eei Dopg liub, ninb Bua Eei maad Zauj lxb. ninb Bua zyav naaig kwavg Jyenq Dopg liub Zyavq pyauj mig a'q.
7.5: Tauj Ryemb yaavb Eei zyavb hog, ninb Bua mivb si-lia myenb Eei Zyavq. Tauj Zyavq ka'Len, maiq pwatg yetg taub myenb yem uaq,
7.16: zwavj myenb zyrug Zwrtq mivb luq si-lia myenb Eei Zyavq. Navq naaig siag mx'q Bwrnq maaig tu'q Eig zinb levb Eaanb. zyepg Mmd mx'q Byaub Baa-li yaag maaig tu'q Eig zinb levb Eaanb. Navq zyruq kxvq Jiaj Eei waag nx.
7.20: za'kevb Zwrtq taaib Navq naaig nx, weig zu'g yem uaq zivb kcvb ninb zu'g zwavj myenb Zaaiq taig mig a'q.
7.17: huvb tiaj Paaiq yem ninb Eei sinb Len uaq taub pcv zuaq zivb kcvb. zuaq kcvb Eei zyavb hog ninb zu'g Zaaiq taig mig a'q, Navq huvb tiaj mivb Tinb huvb Eei myenb Eei pyauq Tinb huvb Eei myenb Jaab Daavg kxvq Eei waag nx.
7.14: ninb Bua zyrug Paaiq i nxm maab Zia Zauj maad mivb zung si-lia Eei pcvb kwanb. huvb tiaj Jaa waag kxvq, “meib Bua mivb mavg kaaj maaib haiq Euvg sig Zwrtq.”
7.4: sij kxvq Bua kxvq, ‘Bua pia'g zivb maa'b!’ yem uaq zivb vxg Naavj, Bua yaag zu'g taig. sij kxvq Bua zweid Jyenq naaiq, Bua yaag zu'g taig. Navq naaig, taaib maa'b! Bua mivb si-lia myenb Eei Zyavq. sij kxvq ninb Bua lyrub Bua Eei mcvg zyrug tu'q zyavb. sij kxvq ninb Bua taij Bua, Bua zyrug zu'g taig.”
7.2: maaib taub huvb tiaj Eei sinb Len pcv kxvq, “mavg maa'b! zyruq pun luvb kcvb Gxi Revg, zuvq maiq haib maaib naaiq Euvg sig saa'b?” e-li-saa tau, “meib kanb Eei mziv tu'q pwatg mq paag meib maiq tu'q Eang yetg teij.”
7.6: weig zu'g zyruq pun si-lia myenb Eei pcv mwavj haid Bx'q Jaaj Eei maab Zia Zauj maad Zauj tomb pcvb kwanb Eei Qiaj Bwi. ninb Bua zyrug laanb Buaj laanb, “mavg maa'b! i-saa-laa-en Eei huvb Zivq hitq-Tai myenb Eei huvb Zauj i-yipq Eei huvb taaib Bx'q Bua.”
7.13: maaib taub ninb Eei Jyen kxvq Buaj huvb tiaj, “pun teij myenb keb pyaa taub yem zivb ka'Euad zevg Fiag Eei maad, mivb mavg kaaj Navq haiq nx. sij kxvq ninb Bua zu'g taig, ninb Bua zyrug Navq yem naaiq zevg Fiag Eei i-saa-laa-en myenb taig nx. se Navq yem naaiq zu'g taig mivb Eei i-saa-laa-en myenb. Toq Paaiq teij myenb mivb mavg kaaj.”
7.12: luvb mwrnd zang huvb tiaj Jiad sin Buaj ninb Eei Jyen, “yia Buaj meib Bua, si-lia myenb Navq haiq nx zruj pun Bua. ninb Bua hiuq tu'q Bua vxg Naavj, ninb Bua zyrug Zwrtq Zyavq pivj Jyenq Zyavq ka'Len. ninb Bua Namq taaib, ‘ninb Bua Dovg haaij zuvq xij Zwrtq zivb.’ ninb Bua zyrug lyemb navb Eei zx'q yia Bua cvj pia'g zivb a'q.”
7.15: ninb Bua zyrug kan Jyenq si-lia pcv mivb Tauj Jx-Dcn Daaib. zyavb tiub Jauq pwatg si-lia myenb kaanq pyauj Eei zyavb hog kwavg Eei lwib hruj Zauj Jaab sig. naaiq teij trug fyenj myenb zyrug Rwrnj mivb Buaj huvb tiaj.
7.11: zuaq kcvb Eei myenb zyrug heug, yaag maaib myenb Buaj Tauj huvb ting.
7.1: mq paag e-li-saa kxvq, “meib Bua mwavj zyruq Eei waag maa'b! zyruq Navq naaiq nx kxvq, ‘Fav Nxi leib maiq ko naaiq nxm zyavb hog, yem saa-maa-lia Eei zivb kcvb, siag mx'q Bwrnq maaig tu'q Eig zinb levb Eaanb. zyepg Mmd mx'q Byaub Baa-li yaag maaig tu'q Eig zinb levb Eaanb.’+”
7.10: ninb Bua zyrug mivb heug zuaq zivb kcvb Eei myenb yaag Buaj ninb Bua, “yia Bua pia'g si-lia myenb Eei Dopg liub Zyavq. maiq pwatg haiq taub myenb yaag maiq haid haiq taub Eei Qiaj Bwi. Kuvj maaib maad Zauj lxb Dob Jyenq uaq. Dopg liub yaag Navq uaq.”

19.18: yaag zx'q ninb Bua Eei zyenb zxi pia'g trud myetg Revg, weig zu'g maiq zeid zyenb, se myenb kanb Eei puad lovg Dyavj, lovg la'pyeiq zruj taaib.
19.8: uaq taub tomb pcvb pyeiq haid kxvq atg-si-lia Eei huvb Zwrtq laa-Kitq zivb, ninb zyrug Twij cvj lxd pwatg huvb tiaj yem lipq-naa zivb Bx'q Jaaj.
19.33: ninb yavb haiq tiub Jauq taaib yaag xij zu'g yavb uaq tiub Jauq Rwrnj. ninb zuvq maiq pia'g naaiq nxm zivb.’ naaiq se zyruq kxvq Eei waag.
19.3: ninb Bua kxvq Buaj i-saa-yaa, “ib Nxi se Dxtq naang, zu'g taanb zu'g Eaiq Eei Nxi. se Navq msia'q txn xij yuvd kub vwaad yaag maiq maaib Qa'q yuvd.
19.32: “weig naaiq zyruq Navq naaiq nx kxvq atg-si-lia Eei huvb. ‘ninb maiq tu'q pia'g naaiq nxm zivb, yaag maiq pwrnq yetg Ritq fxv pia'g. ninb maiq tu'q nanq Txvb paaib yem naaiq nxm zivb Eei Ra'Myen, yaag maiq tu'q Dwi nia Lav weib kxmj Bx'q zivb.
19.21: naaiq se zyruq Eei waag kxvq ninb. “+‘maiq pweij Jiaj txn Eei sia'q, si-on, mavg Piaj meib, Wrtq meib. ye-lu-saa-lem Eei sia'q pwatg meib pyauj yaag Wavj mGxvq pun meib.
19.35: uaq mwrnd zyruq Eei finb myenb Zwrtq mivb yem atg-si-lia myenb Eei Zyavq taij yetg sinj Yetg waang pyaa Zin taub myenb taig. ta'Eeig Dxm Ryruq Eei myenb Jiad sin taaib pwatg penj Janb taig Eei sei Revg mig a'q.
19.14: he-se-Ki-yaa to'g liud trug fyenj myenb txb taaib Eei fyenj, ninb zyrug pia'g zavg zyruq Eei pyauq Kxi fyenj an Jyenq zyruq Eei Ra'Myen.
19.23: meib lovg meib Eei trug fyenj myenb Ki zyruq. meib kxvq, “yia lovg yia Bx'q Jaaj Eei maab Zia Zamq faauj Lav haig Eei Bov, zuvq pia'g le-Baa-nxn Do Jiaj Eei txvj. yia kxij kaub Lav Jiaj Eei sij-Daa zovb Dyavj, yaag kxij kaub lovj Jiaj Eei zovb. yia pia'g lomg Tauj kaub ko Jiaj Eei txvj, pia'g Tauj kaub hod Jiaj Eei kemb.
19.6: i-saa-yaa kxvq Buaj ninb Bua, “xij zu'g Buaj meib Bua Eei zyruq, ‘zyruq Navq naaiq nx kxvq. maiq tuvq kamb Riaj meib Bua haid liud naaiq teij waag, tovb atg-si-lia Eei huvb Eei pru kxvq Ki yia Eei waag.
19.34: ‘weig yia kanb yaag weig yia Eei pru, Daa-witq, yia xij peu Jyenq naaiq nxm zivb, yaag xij Fruj naaiq nxm zivb.’+”
19.2: ninb Paaiq kruj huvb ting uaq taub e-li-yaa-Kim Zauj sepq-naa srub piuq Zauj zruj kaub Lo uaq teij sai myenb, yetg zuvq zu'q Jyenq la'maab Diab Zru, mivb lxd aa-mxtq Eei txn, trug waag myenb, i-saa-yaa.
19.36: atg-si-lia Eei huvb, sen-naa-Ke-lipq, zyrug Twij Gxi Rwrnj pyauq yem ni-naa-we.
19.20: aa-mxtq Eei txn, i-saa-yaa, pun waag mivb Buaj he-se-Ki-yaa, “zyruq, i-saa-laa-en myenb Eei Tinb huvb, Navq naaiq nx kxvq, ‘meib tauj kauj kxvq Tauj atg-si-lia Eei huvb, sen-naa-Ke-lipq, uaq teij waag yia haid mig a'q.’
19.24: yia yem kanb nxm teib puv wetq uamb Kwrtq yaag yem uaq hopq uam. yia lovg yia Eei zaub penq Zaaiq Gaai i-yipq teib puv Eei yetg zuvq Do'q.’+”
19.28: laaij meib Qiaj Jiad nrud yia, kxvq yia, meib puvj Eei waab mauj yaag Tauj yia Eei mnxmb, yia zyrug lovg yia Eei Lia'g vau, vau Jyenq meib Eei Ba'zxv, yaag zx'q yia Eei hanb Kruq fapq meib Eei Rwib, pun meib taauj Gaav Rwrnj meib taaib Eei Jauq.’
19.7: yia xij pun ninb maaib Euvg Hruq. ninb tu'q haid Euvg waab Ryaauj zyrug Rwrnj ninb kanb Eei teib puv. yem ninb kanb Eei pwrnb teib puv, yia zuvq pun ninb zu'g Ru'g Daauq taij taig.’+”
19.29: “o he-se-Ki-yaa aa'b! naaiq se zruj nxm Javb hog. “ib Havj meib Bua tu'q Eang ninb kanb Zwrtq Eei ka'naaiq, ta'Eeig Havj tu'q Eang yem uaq teij Lo taaib Eei ka'naaiq. mq paag ta'faam Havj xij zu'g zwavj yaag xij zu'g syru, xij zu'g zwavj a'vung Wivj yaag Eang uaq teij pyruq.
19.19: o zyruq, yia Bua Eei Tinb huvb aag, Toq Fruj yia Bua pyauj Dutq atg-si-lia huvb Eei puab Diaq weig pun luvb Diaq maang kua'q hiuq tu'q meib, zyruq kanb, se Tinb huvb.”
19.17: “o zyruq aag, za'kevb zyen Eei. atg-si-lia Eei huvb paaig Waav naaiq teij maang kua'q yaag pun ninb Bua Eei teib puv Waav Revg,
19.31: weig zu'g maaib teij zevg Fiag Eei myenb xij yem ye-lu-saa-lem Zwrtq, maaib kwanb tu'q mcvg Zwrtq Eei myenb xij yem si-on Bov Zwrtq. nrnb Jiaj Eei zyruq Dovg haaij zuvq xij Navq naaiq nx zruj.
19.30: yu-Daa Eei trub zov tu'q pyauj Dutq zevg Fiag Eei myenb, cvj haib yem naaig Navq ka'naaib zwavj Fiag Ruvb, Yaavj taaib zyavb pyruq.
19.27: “+‘mq paag yia hiuq tu'q meib yem haaij, yaag hiuq tu'q meib haiq zang Zwrtq mivb cvj pia'g taaib, yia yaag hiuq meib Qiaj Jiad, nrud yia, kxvq yia.
19.11: meib yaag haid kxvq atg-si-lia Eei zwavj huvb Navq haiq nx zruj pun maang kua'q, zuvq myetg Revg mig a'q. meib Namq taaib meib haib tu'q Fruj fai?
19.5: he-se-Ki-yaa Eei Jyen mivb Tauj i-saa-yaa uaq,
19.9: atg-si-lia Eei huvb haid fyenj kxvq, i-yipq teib puv, Kutq myenb Eei huvb, Ti-laa-haa-Kaa, Zwrtq taaib xij Zauj ninb Bx'q Jaaj. ninb zyrug Paaiq trug fyenj myenb mivb he-se-Ki-yaa uaq Navq naaiq nx kxvq,
19.16: o zyruq aag, Toq pcv mnxmb mwavj. o zyruq aag, Toq nuvj Gxi mziv mavg. mwavj sen-naa-Ke-lipq fuvj taaib Ki zyavb Jyenq Eei Tinb huvb Eei waag.
19.37: maaib Nxi ninb yem miub pyauq ka'Euad paaij ninb Eei zyenb, nitq-lokq, uaq zang, i taub ninb Eei txn, atg-lam-me-lekq Zauj saa-le-se, lovg Ru'g Daauq taij ninb. Ga'haaq ninb Bua pyauj mivb yem aa-laa-latq teib puv. sen-naa-Ke-lipq Eei txn, e-saanj-hatq-Don, Ripg Jyenq ninb zruj huvb.
19.4: Riaj zyruq, meib Eei Tinb huvb, mwavj haid uaq taub tomb pcvb pyeiq, tovb ninb Eei zyruq, atg-si-lia Eei huvb, Paaiq taaib Ki zyavb Jyenq Eei Tinb huvb uaq teij waag. zyruq, meib Eei Tinb huvb, zyrug weig ninb haid naaiq teij waag kxvq ninb a'q. weig naaiq Toq meib Tevj naaiq teij zevg Fiag Eei myenb tauj kauj.”
19.10: “xij zu'g kxvq Buaj yu-Daa Eei huvb, he-se-Ki-yaa, ‘meib Bua syenj Kauj Eei Tinb huvb kxvq, “ye-lu-saa-lem maiq zu'g Jiu pun atg-si-lia huvb” ninb Kuvj Duaq meib Bua Navq. maiq tuvq mwavj.
19.22: meib kxvq to'g Ki haiq taub? meib lovg meib Eei Qiaj kxvq haiq taub? meib nuvj meib Eei mziv zruj mauj pun haiq taub? meib zruj pun i-saa-laa-en Eei Zivb Revg zyruq.
19.12: uaq teij nxmb nxm kua'q Eei taub taub zyenb haib Fruj tu'q ninb Bua fai? se yia Eei ovb Taaij myetg uaq teij kua'q Eei zyenb, tovb ko-saan, haa-laan, le-sepq Zauj yem Ten-atg-saaj Eei e-Den myenb Eei zyenb.
19.15: he-se-Ki-yaa tauj kauj kxvq Buaj zyruq, “o zyruq, i-saa-laa-en Eei Tinb huvb, tovb yem uaq teij i taub Ke-lu-Bim Bu'Dovj uaq taub aa'b! Kuvj meib kanb zruj luvb Diaq maang kua'q Eei Tinb huvb. meib zeij luvb zeij Dau.
19.13: haa-matq Eei huvb, aan-patg Eei huvb, sej-faan-waa-im zivb Eei huvb fai he-naa Eei huvb fai ipg-waa Eei huvb yem haaij?’+”
19.1: he-se-Ki-yaa huvb haid liud uaq taub tomb pcvb pyeiq kxvq Eei waag, ninb petq ninb Eei lwi cvj zu'q Jyenq la'maab Diab Zru pia'g zavg zyruq Eei pyauq.
19.26: naaiq teij zivb Eei pc'g fivj Eei Qa'q Revg mig a'q. ninb Bua zyrug Hruq waaig Revg yaag zu'g Eaiq. ninb Bua se Navq yem Daub Waav Eei miaq, Navq miab yaav lunj Eei nx, se Navq yem pyaub vxb Zwrtq taaib Eei miaq, maiq kcvb Lo, zu'g Eutg trud puaq Gaai.

17.3: atg-si-lia Eei huvb, scn-maa-ne-sej, taaib Bx'q ninb, mq paag ho-se-yaa Eyemg mau, Havb Havj yaag pun Eaanb ninb.

17.40: mq paag ninb Bua maiq mwavj. ninb Bua kan zinb Daavg Eei Jauq zruj.
17.14: mq paag ninb Bua maiq mwavj. ninb Bua Hruq vcvg Navq ninb Bua Eei ovb Taaij, maiq syenj Kauj zyruq, ninb Bua Eei Tinb huvb.
17.23: Tauj Ga'haaq zyruq zung ninb Bua Zwrtq, maiq pun yem ninb Eei Ra'Myen, Navq ninb lovg ninb Eei pru, zwavj trug waag myenb, kxvq Eei waag nx. i-saa-laa-en myenb zyrug yem kanb Eei teib puv zu'g kwaatq mivb Tauj atg-si-lia teib puv, Zxg yem naaig Tauj ib Jaaj Nxi.
17.6: ho-se-yaa zruj huvb ta'Juaq Havj uaq Havj, atg-si-lia Eei huvb Zaavq tu'q saa-maa-lia. ninb kwaatq i-saa-laa-en myenb mivb atg-si-lia, pun ninb Bua yem haa-laa-aa zivb Zauj haa-Bo Daaib Len Eei ko-saan Zauj mi-Dia myenb Eei zivb.
17.34: Tauj ib Jaaj Nxi ninb Bua Zxg kan zinb Daavg Eei lob leid zruj. ninb Bua maiq zavg zyruq yaag maiq ei Jyenq zyruq Jiu pun yaa-Kopq Eei zeib fun Eei livg Zauj leib latg Zauj leid Zauj hatg Eei waag, tovb ninb Zwrtq Buaj heug i-saa-laa-en, Eei zeib fun.
17.2: ziuj zyruq mavg, ninb zruj waaig sig mq paag maiq Navq zinb Daavg uaq teij i-saa-laa-en huvb.
17.36: meib Bua xij zu'g zavg zyruq, tovb suv Zwrtq ninb henq haig Eei puad lovg tomb Qa'q txb meib Bua Zwrtq i-yipq teib puv. xij zu'g kweig Fiag paaij ninb, fovg hxg ziag pun ninb.
17.20: zyruq zyrug Gemb i-saa-laa-en myenb Eei zwavj pc'g fivj, pun ninb Bua zu'g Kruq yaag zx'q ninb Bua Jiu pun Zaavq ninb Bua uaq teij myenb Eei puab Diaq, zung ninb Bua Zwrtq ninb Eei Ra'Myen.
17.24: atg-si-lia Eei huvb syru yem Baa-Bi-lon, Ku-Taa, apg-waa, haa-matq Zauj sej-faan-waa-im Eei myenb mivb lyepg vwaab kxn yem saa-maa-lia Eei muvq tiq i-saa-laa-en myenb. ninb Bua zyrug tu'q Revg saa-maa-lia yaag yem saa-maa-lia Eei nxmb nxm muvq.
17.28: maaib taub yem saa-maa-lia zu'g kwaatq mivb Eei sai myenb zyrug mivb yem Betg-en Faauj ninb Bua Navq haiq nx zavg zyruq.
17.7: naaiq teij yetg zuvq sig Zwrtq taaib weig zu'g i-saa-laa-en myenb paamd zwid txvg zyruq, ninb Bua Eei Tinb huvb, tovb txb ninb Bua Zwrtq i-yipq teib puv, leib Dutq i-yipq Eei faa-lo huvb Eei puab Diaq. ninb Bua zavg Eiag Eei zyenb
17.29: mq paag fivb fivj myenb Zxg zeij ninb Bua kanb Eei zyenb, xn Jyenq saa-maa-lia myenb zruj taaib yem Lav zavg zyenb Eei nxmb nxm txvj.
17.19: lyemb yu-Daa yaag maiq ei zyruq, ninb Bua Eei Tinb huvb Eei leib latg. ninb Bua kan i-saa-laa-en myenb lyepg taaib Eei leid.
17.17: ninb Bua zx'q ninb Bua Eei naamb Erud lovg trud puaq ziag fovg hxg. ninb Bua Bruq kwaaj, zruj faatq, yaag maaig kanb ziuj zyruq mavg zruj waaig sig, Zua'q zyruq Qiaj Jiad haig.
17.38: maiq tuvq la'Ku'q yia Zauj meib Bua lyepg Eei vcvg waag, yaag maiq tuvq zavg Eiag Eei zyenb.
17.31: apg-waa myenb zeij nipq-hatg Zauj Taan-Takq zyenb Eei favj, sej-faan-waa-im myenb lovg trud puaq ninb Bua Eei fu'Jweiq pun sej-faan-waa-im Eei zyenb, atg-lam-me-lekq Zauj aa-nam-me-lekq.
17.30: Baa-Bi-lon myenb zeij sukg-Kotq-Be-notq zyenb Eei favj, Ku-Taa myenb zeij ne-kan zyenb Eei favj, haa-matq myenb zeij aa-si-maa zyenb Eei favj.

11.5: ninb yaag Paaiq zyavj ninb Bua, “meib Bua xij zu'g Navq naaiq nx zruj. ta'faanb tivb kov Nxi lwrnb paan zuaq uaq kwanb pcv Eei pua kruq Eei yetg kruq xij zu'g zuaq huvb ting,
11.16: ninb Bua zyrug zx'q huvb maag mivb Tauj huvb ting, maad pia'g Eei kcvb uaq nxm txvj, pun ninb zu'g taij taig.
11.20: kua'q zavg Eei zwavj pc'g fivj zyrug Fyenb yrub. zivb ka'Euad Taaib pcvb a'q. weig zu'g aa-Taa-li-yaa huvb maag yem huvb ting zu'g Ru'g Daauq taij taig mig a'q.

11.14: ninb mavg zyrug pwatg huvb tiaj ei Jyenq leid sruq Dyrub ka'Len. pcvb pyeiq Zauj pyomq Ratg Eei myenb yaag sruq Jyenq huvb tiaj Eei ka'Len. teib puv Eei zwavj pc'g fivj Fyenb yrub haig yaag pyomq Ratg. aa-Taa-li-yaa zyrug petq ninb Eei lwi yaag heug Zwrtq taaib kxvq, “peig sib aaq lo'b! peig sib aaq lo'b!”
11.4: Tauj ta'Zyetq Havj uaq Havj, ye-ho-yaa-Daa sai myenb heug Kaa-li myenb Eei pcvb pyeiq Zauj kruj huvb tiaj Eei pcv taaib yaag txb ninb Bua pia'g zavg zyruq Eei pyauq. ninb Zauj ninb Bua lyepg vcvg waag yaag pun ninb Bua yem zyruq Eei pyauq hruq waag. Ga'haaq ninb txb huvb Eei txn taaib pun ninb Bua mavg.
11.21: yo-aatg faauj weig zruj huvb uaq zang, ninb Eei Havb Jeiq tu'q siag Havj.
11.2: mq paag yo-lam Eei sia'q, aa-hatg-yaa Eei muag, ye-ho-Qe-Baa, zx'q aa-hatg-yaa Eei txn, yo-aatg, yem xij zu'g taij taig Eei huvb txn Bu'Dovj nimg Zwrtq taaib. ninb txb yo-aatg Zauj txb yo-aatg uaq taub pru mivb pivj Jyenq zavg Tinb huvb Eei pyauq Eei yetg Qovj ken, weig pyauj Dutq, maiq zu'g aa-Taa-li-yaa huvb maag taij.
11.6: pua kruq Eei yetg kruq xij zu'g zuaq suj-e kcvb, pua kruq Eei yetg kruq xij zu'g yem zuaq huvb ting Eei pcv Ga'haaq Gaav Eei kcvb.
11.13: aa-Taa-li-yaa mwavj haid uaq teij kruj huvb tiaj Eei pcv Zauj zwavj pc'g fivj Eei Qiaj Bwi, ninb zyrug mivb Tauj zavg zyruq Eei pyauq, pc'g fivj uaq.
11.12: ye-ho-yaa-Daa sai myenb txb huvb tiaj Eei txn Zwrtq taaib yaag zx'q huvb nivq Tevj ninb Dovj Jyenq. ninb Bua zx'q lcvd vcvg waag sru Jiu pun ninb zyrug xn ninb zruj huvb, cvj lovg xn myenb Eei yrub toj Jyenq. zwavj myenb zyrug Baij puad heug Jyenq kxvq, “Toq pun huvb tiaj zyavb tu'q maang fwij.”
11.15: ye-ho-yaa-Daa sai myenb Paaiq pcvb kwanb Eei pcvb pyeiq, “txb huvb maag kan pcv weib Jyenq Eei txvj Zwrtq taaib. haiq taub kan Jyenq xij Tevj ninb yaag xij zu'g lovg Ru'g Daauq taij uaq taub taig.” weig zu'g sai myenb kxvq Jiaj, “maiq tuvq yem zavg zyruq Eei pyauq pun ninb zu'g taij taig.”
11.11: kruj huvb tiaj Eei pcv, kx'g myenb Eei puad nanq Jyenq ua'g king yem ziab txvb Zauj zavg zyruq Eei pyauq zaaij puv Zauj Byaaug puv weib Jyenq huvb tiaj.
11.1: aa-hatg-yaa Eei maa, aa-Taa-li-yaa, pwatg ninb Eei txn taig mig a'q, ninb zyrug Jiad kxn taij Revg maaib huvb trub Eei myenb.
11.10: ye-ho-yaa-Daa zx'q yem zavg zyruq Eei pyauq zinb Daavg penj Daa-witq huvb Eei Zav Zauj Txvb paaib pun zwavj pcvb pyeiq.

5.18: mq paag Toq zyruq kwavg yia, meib Eei pru, zruj Eei naaiq yetg Euvg sig. se yia Eei zyruq pia'g lim-mon zyenb Eei miub pyauq Do'q Fiag paaij Eei zyavb hog, ninb yaag pavg yia Eei puad pia'g, yia yaag yem uaq Do'q Fiag. yia yem lim-mon Eei miub pyauq Do'q Fiag Eei zyavb hog, Toq zyruq kwavg Gxi yia, meib Eei pru, Eei zwid.”
5.8: Tinb huvb Eei myenb, e-li-saa, haid kxvq huvb tiaj petq ninb Eei lwi, ninb zyrug Paaiq myenb mivb kxvq, “meib weig haiq tiug petq meib Eei lwi? kunq heug naaig taub myenb taaib yia naaiq. ninb zyrug hiuq tu'q yem i-saa-laa-en teib puv maaib taub trug waag myenb.”

5.14: naa-aa-maan zyrug ei Jyenq Tinb huvb Eei myenb Eei waag Fiag Jx-Dcn Daaib zyemj siag Rung. ninb Eei xq zyrug Rwrnj lod Navq fu'Jweiq Eei xq nx, ninb yaag Zivb Revg mig a'q.

5.24: Tauj Bovb aiq, ke-haa-si zx'q pru Daam Eei ka'naaiq Yetq Jyenq pyauq zyrug heug uaq teij pru Rwrnj. ninb Bua yaag Rwrnj mig a'q.
5.7: i-saa-laa-en Eei huvb to'g liud naaiq zeiq fyenj, ninb petq ninb Eei lwi yaag kxvq, “yia zruj Tinb huvb? haib pun myenb taig, pun myenb navb fai? naaiq taub myenb Zivj fuvj fyenj heug yia zxg naaiq taub myenb Eei komb huq pcvg lovj. mavg maa'b! ninb Kuvj lxd sig Zauj yia Rcv Navq.”
5.19: e-li-saa kxvq, “meib kunq pcvb xn Eei Rwrnj.” naa-aa-maan Zwrtq Jauq mivb maiq kcvb ko Dovg haaij,
5.17: naa-aa-maan kxvq, “meib za'kevb maiq lovg nx, Toq meib pun kauj i taub lxb Tx Eei nia yia, meib Eei pru, weig zu'g yem naaiq mivb meib Eei pru maiq fovg hxg puaq ziag Eei ka'naaiq fai lovg haiq Euvg ziag haiq taub zyenb Zwrtq liud ziag pun zyruq.
5.27: weig naaiq naa-aa-maan Eei komb huq pcvg zyrug Jiaj meib Zauj meib Eei zeib fun yetg liud xij putq.” ke-haa-si zyrug yem e-li-saa Eei Ra'Myen Zwrtq mivb. ninb putq komb huq pcvg. ninb Eei Dopq Bopq pc'g Eei, Navq sxv nx.
5.11: mq paag naa-aa-maan Qiaj Jiad Jyenq mivb mig a'q. ninb kxvq, “yia laaig ninb xij Zwrtq taaib lxd yia, sruq Jyenq tauj kauj heug zyruq, ninb Eei Tinb huvb, Eei Buaj, yaag Wavj puad yem putq pcvg Eei txvj kub vwaaig, zxg yia Eei komb huq pcvg lovj.

5.4: naa-aa-maan zyrug mivb Buaj ninb Eei zyruq, si-lia Eei huvb tiaj, uaq taub i-saa-laa-en sia'q Navq haiq nx kxvq,
5.10: e-li-saa heug taub trug fyenj myenb Zwrtq mivb Buaj naa-aa-maan, “mivb Jx-Dcn Daaib Raauj siag Rung sin. meib Eei xq zyrug lovj Navq lod uaq nx. meib yaag Zivb Revg mig a'q.”
5.22: ke-haa-si tau, “maiq maaib haiq Euvg lx'g. yia Eei zyruq Paaiq yia taaib kxvq, ‘a'Jav maaib i taub uaq kwanb trug waag myenb Eei myenb lunj myenb yem e-faa-im Eei Bovb aiq txvj taaib. Toq pun Eig zyepg yetq Jxib Eaanb ninb Bua Zauj i yemg lwib hruj.’+”
5.12: Daa-matq-katg Eei Daaib, aa-Baa-naa Zauj faan-paa, maiq zeid kaub lovj i-saa-laa-en Eei tiub tiub uam fai? yia yem uaq Raauj yaag haib tu'q Zivb Revg taaib maiq zeid?” ninb zyrug taauj sin Qiaj Jiad Jyenq mivb mig a'q.
5.15: naa-aa-maan Zauj kan ninb Eei yetg zuvq myenb Rwrnj Tauj Tinb huvb Eei myenb uaq, sruq Jyenq e-li-saa Eei Ra'Myen kxvq, “ib zang yia hiuq tu'q yem luvb Diaq maiq maaib Tinb huvb Zwrtq liud yem i-saa-laa-en teib puv. ib zang Toq zipq yia, meib Eei pru, xij Jiu pun Eei zivb Eeig.”
5.13: mq paag naa-aa-maan Eei pru mivb Tauj ninb Eei Ra'Myen kxvq, “tomb kxj aag, sij kxvq uaq taub trug waag myenb heug meib zruj yetg Euvg Lo Eei sig, tomb kxj mtaaib zruj Eei maiq zeid? Navq naaig, ninb Buaj tomb kxj, ‘mivb Raauj zyrug Zivb Revg a'q,’ maiq zeid kaub xij zu'g zruj fai?”
5.1: naa-aa-maan zruj si-lia huvb Eei tomb pcvb pyeiq. ninb Eei zyruq funj ninb zruj lovg Jyenq Eei myenb yaag Taaib ninb, weig zu'g zyruq lovg ninb Tevj si-lia kua'q tu'q hivb. ninb penj yetg taub Bx'q Jaaj henq Eei myenb, mq paag ninb putq komb huq pcvg.

9.32: ye-hu Zau mGxvq mavg uaq fov mwrnb kxvq, “haiq taub yem yia naaiq puv? maaib haiq taub?” maaib i pua taub Jyen yem uaq fov mwrnb mavg Jyenq ninb.
9.21: yo-lam kxvq, “xij zu'g liug leid mivb a'q. ninb Bua zyrug liug leid zyavj ninb Eei maab Zia. i-saa-laa-en Eei huvb, yo-lam Zauj yu-Daa Eei huvb, aa-hatg-yaa, kx'g myenb pia'g kx'g myenb Eei Zia Zwrtq mivb pwavb ye-hu. ninb Bua zyrug yem yitq-le-en myenb, naa-Botg, Eei Dau, pwavb Jaaj.

10.19: ib zang xij zu'g heug Baa-an Eei trug waag myenb yetg zuvq Zauj zavg Baa-an Eei zwavj myenb Zauj zwavj sai myenb taaib zunq yia naaiq. maiq tuvq pun Zaa yetg taub weig zu'g yia xij zruj Lo Eei ziag pun Baa-an. haiq taub maiq taaib, uaq taub zuvq maiq haib tu'q mcvg zyavb.” mq paag ye-hu taaq kuq kwaij Eei za'eij weig taij zavg Baa-an zyenb Eei myenb.
